{
  "stem": "1062.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it wasn't-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't a web.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just want to bring out how people used to make their own clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, from the flags they made not a web.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was called-- like, weaving. weaving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would set up in the house like, weaving.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a whole-- it took up, like, the whole living room there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would set it up, and then they would take old rags, whatever they had left over, and they would weave it into this thing with the flags, you know?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You make carpets out of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you didn't want to make carpets, then they would weave this material, and they would make clothes out of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's flax seed clothes, it's like a very rough-- it looks like denim.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe my village was 50 years ahead of the times because they made denim there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was-- it was-- this-- they used to make their own clothes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then from, from the sheep, they would make shoes where they would put a lot of rags in with the skin, make shoes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And not necessarily the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Jewish people were more, were more-- you know, they, they would dress a little-- not different, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I'm just talking the local people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the life was very good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, compared to what was coming, it was good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because what's happening now is this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] I don't want to get into politics, but we all know, you know, in Russia, there was the Soviet Union, and they had their interest in Nazi Germany and [?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Nottingham. ?] And the British and the French, you know, they would appease us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know the whole story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But what happens is in 1939, Germany invades Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
